{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji14.pdf"],"article":{"title":"复朱德等电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"复朱德等电!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年3月19日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今后八路军坚守平顺、漳河线，不再退让；卫立煌表示希望与朱、彭会谈，请考虑择地与卫会谈。如决定，请将陕甘宁边区、扩军补充、增饷、新军、河北及操之过急东进攻新四军各问题全盘提出，托他转告蒋介石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和王稼祥复朱德、彭德怀、杨尚昆电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1940,"month":3,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":487,"page_end":487},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}